abstract: Tatjana Maria of Germany defeats Eugenie Bouchard of Canada, 6-0, 7-6, in opening match of Miami Open; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Eugenie Bouchard of Canada was upset in her opening match at the Miami Open in Key Biscayne, Fla., by the qualifier Tatjana Maria of Germany, 6-0, 7-6 (4).

headline.main: Eugenie Bouchard Falls Early in Florida
